    "# Installing Scikit-learn\n",
    "\n",
    "Open your **terminal** *(or use **Jupyter Notebook** / **Google Colab**)* and run:\n",
    "\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "pip install scikit-learn\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "# Or in Google Colab\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "!pip install scikit-learn\n",
    "```"
